{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "靜候駕臨", "storyInfo": "諾伯特區中的格拉斯哥幫在新首領卡鐸爾的領導下艱難保全著他們的拳館。被監視的戈爾丁只能委託茉莉去警告自救軍及時轉移。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g1_glasgowboxinggym", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "r", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1", "focus": "l", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，這裡暫且安全。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡鐸爾，外面還是一團糟。我們確實已經不在倫蒂尼姆了，老卸貨塔的塔頂應該能看到地塊外的情況，但我接近不了，那在封鎖區外。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜就算看到了，也沒什麼意義，薩卡茲看得很嚴，他們的人數......相當多。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#5$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#5$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這人怎麼回事？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，想找薩卡茲談條件。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果呢？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己看。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g1_glasgowboxinggym", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "包紮好了，我只能做到這個程度了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝......謝謝你們。", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天哪，為什麼......到底發生了什麼？", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還能發生什麼？薩卡茲已經在倫蒂尼姆城裡待了四年了。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會至今還以為他們是被可憐鬼卡文迪許請過來做客的吧？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他們從來都沒有......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們從來都沒有什麼？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你一定是從不出門的貴族老爺，連早餐的瘤奶都需要僕人為你送到餐桌上。嘿，你怎麼會淪落到我們諾伯特區來的。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，我是個學者，只是經濟上暫時有些麻煩......只要把手上的書稿寫完，應該就能......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，我甚至沒來得及把稿子帶出書房！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德，你真的很擅長找到些落魄鬼。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放尊重些，如果順利，我很有可能是皇家科學院的下一個院士！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“很有可能”，哼。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是不明白，新聞裡不總說......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“一切太平”。你還想在廣播裡聽到什麼？“市民朋友們，很遺憾，倫蒂尼姆如今是個糞坑”？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾年前派去各個報社和電視台的那些“特別指導專員”可不是白拿工資的。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看過海布里區那些軍工廠上現在飄著的是誰的旗幟？那奧克特里格區前幾天的那場大火你總該記得吧。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可，戰爭......城防軍呢？大公爵們呢？他們不是應該已經在倫蒂尼姆周圍保護我們了嗎？", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼就......薩卡茲們打不過大公爵的，對吧？那些魔族佬不過是一群縮在荒地上的野蠻人，可維多利亞是這片大地上最偉大的國家！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰告訴你的？一邊在家裡吃甜麵包一邊突然領悟到的嗎？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正我在被條子按在牆上搜身的時候，可從沒感覺到過這一點。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，“下個院士”，走吧，你不適合跟我們混在一起。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可......可我該去哪？", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的公寓不在這片封鎖區裡，我忠誠的傭人也不知道去哪了......我在這誰也不認識。", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會幹什麼？醫療，縫紉，維修，或者別的什麼都好。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，我的研究方向是紋章學......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們就沒有研究把空氣變成肉排的學問嗎？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個......雖然不是我的學術方向，但可能是有一些難度......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德，你不能再撿這些老爺們回來了，他甚至連玩笑都聽不明白。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的物資儲備畢竟是有限的。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......要不，去幫戴菲恩管倉庫？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德！你又想把麻煩事都甩給我！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我總不能就看著他死在大街上。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這種時刻，我們更需要團結。多個人總是多份力量。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“團結”......唉。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議會和大公爵們該向你們學學這點，否則我們也不會淪落到今天。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們怎麼不團結？在吊死國王這件事上就團結得很呢。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時......唉，算了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你能派上點用場，“下個院士”先生。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定盡力！不過，說起來......你們是？", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，歡迎來到“揍歪下巴”拳館！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#4$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也可以叫我們格拉斯哥幫。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "海蒂，你還好嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "事實上，我並不知道你最近在哪裡，自從開書店的亞當斯先生死後，我已經有些日子沒能聯繫上你了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我已經很久沒有繼續我們的工作了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "請原諒我，我親愛的朋友，我從不會向你隱瞞什麼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但我確實十分......迷茫。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾告訴我，和平一定會再次到來......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我沒法再用虛假的希望欺騙自己，我沒法再躲進房間中，假裝我們所做的一切仍然有意義。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，或許我們可以試著用一種更加長遠的眼光，“歷史的維度”......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，和平會到來，和平終會到來。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而戰爭，也一定會更加殘忍地擊碎它。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾相信我們能贏，我依然懇求我們能贏。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，海蒂，如果我們所做的一切，最終只是些自我安慰和自我寬解......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是如果。或許這已經是事實......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些書本，這幾張課桌，這個搖搖欲墜的學校......怎麼能對抗一個時代？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海蒂，我沒辦法......我幾乎沒辦法繼續堅持。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該怎麼辦？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，您還好嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉......你回來了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在寫信嗎？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這些什麼也不是。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......突然想起了幾本以前看過的小說。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主角往往是風流倜儻的軍官，穿著得體的軍服，叼著煙斗奔赴前線。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但作者永遠都不會告訴我們，到底是哪一片戰場，戰壕裡的氣味又是怎樣。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戀慕著主人公的先生或者小姐們聚在一起，吃著精緻的茶點，懷著一顆惴惴不安的心——", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#7$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我們都知道，這只是些文學技巧，最終的結局總是團圓。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍有追求的作者會試圖營造一種被這裡的評論家們稱作“深刻”的氛圍。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "故事中會點綴著一些可控的死亡，往往是主人公的戰友，他們為了掩護英雄倒在了前線的壕溝裡。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，那些兇殘的敵人會被主人公手刃，正義與道德再一次得到彰顯。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在戰友哀傷的葬禮上，代表榮耀的花瓣灑滿棺槨，人群肅穆，獻上總結他們偉大事業的悼詞。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻是絕佳的煽情點，主人公們會手握著手，擦去淚花，堅定地望向天邊的朝陽——", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會說，希望終會來臨，一切犧牲都有意義。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，作者可以在這裡停下了，真正美好的未來就交給讀者們去想像吧，最後的莊嚴感足夠讓他們滿足了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您居然還讀過這樣的小說。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是很多年前了，誰沒有經歷過那樣的年紀呢。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我還是個少女的時候，一度十分迷戀這些書......我並不對主人公們抱有太多感情，但那些死亡確實讓我迷戀。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我偶爾會想像自己是那位為事業獻上生命的英雄，人們含著眼淚，誇讚我所創造的時代，或者，最起碼，稱頌我的犧牲......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，很幼稚。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再後來，我自以為自己已經足夠清醒，足夠看穿這些裹著糖霜的幻想。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我開始發現......我與當年，或許沒有本質上的不同。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說，您以前和孩子們說過，死亡是個嚴肅的話題。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈，是嗎？我不記得了。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概只是些我習以為常的老套說教吧。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的採購順利嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，街上的情況並沒有很糟，商店裡的東西也沒有漲價。只是城防軍好像比以往多了些。薩卡茲士兵們......也不再遮遮掩掩。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，大家都在假裝什麼都沒有發生。除了......原本是諾伯特區的地方，如今只剩下周圍區塊延伸過來的支撐骨架。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那些地方呢？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，我要再次向你道歉，我不該把你牽扯進這些事裡，只是......萊托已經盯上了我，每次我出門都有幾個不懷好意的人跟著。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#5$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能賭一把，賭你還不在他們的監視名單上。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我很高興能為倫蒂尼姆的大家出一份力。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，您所說的幾個地點，現在都冷冷清清的，那些接頭暗號我都用了，也沒有人回應。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......也許他們已經放棄了？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，他們比我堅強得多。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我發現了一封信，應該是留給您的，我沒拆。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......不，這不是他們的筆跡。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......信裡詳細寫了自救軍情報交換站的幾乎全部資訊。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說什麼？！可是，怎麼會......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#4$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一次威脅。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......對我們掌握得很徹底。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那......戈爾丁女士，那我們該怎麼辦？！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#2$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "茉莉，我會再給你一份地點列表。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有直接去過這些據點，但我分析過情報的流向，他們......應該就在那裡。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不該這麼冒險，這違反了工作守則，但是......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這消息對自救軍很重要，對吧？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這關乎很多人的性命。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們就應該去做。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#6$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......茉莉，像我教你的那樣，留意所有可能的尾隨者，不論跟著你的人是不是薩卡茲，都不要掉以輕心。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡找到一個叫克洛維希婭的女孩，或者任何能聯繫到克洛維希婭的人，告訴他們，整個情報網洩漏了，他們需要馬上轉移！", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#6$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戈爾丁女士，您要去哪？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托的辦公室。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會盡量為你們爭取時間。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是——", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，我不會有事的，我......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願我比自己想像的要強大。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我做了一個夢。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我夢見......陰雲籠罩了這座城市，沾血的薩卡茲旗幟在每一座建築上空飄揚，而城外......源石簇長滿了目力所及的每一個角落。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我夢見鏽色的王座在大地上矗立，人們跪拜，流下黑色的眼淚；我夢見王座上的人輕揮手臂，呐喊聲便刺破了整片天空。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，王座的陰影裡，瑟縮的人們悄悄抬起頭......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感受到他們的感情......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知該怎麼描述......那麼駁雜，那麼壓抑......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能辨別出浮在最表面的那些，那種痛苦......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還有仇恨。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王座上的人......是誰？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是薩卡茲眾魂預見的未來嗎？還是，一位魔王的使命？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐是不是也做過這個夢？會不會......這就是她現在所期盼的場景？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不會的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，這個夢......它什麼都不是，對嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你最近太累了。;夢只是夢而已。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line318", "option2": "line318"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......謝謝你，博士。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#21$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，那只是一個夢......而已......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，博士。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生好些了嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#19$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不上好，她的身體......本就稱得上瘦弱。傷口很深。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#5$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈已經嘗試了幾種辦法，但效果都很有限，她還沒有甦醒。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#5$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Mon3tr看起來在緩慢地自我修復，我們同樣不知道它能恢復到什麼程度，乃至它是否能真正恢復。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#5$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......博士，城防軍指揮塔上，如果我能......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#18$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "每個人都已經做到了最好。;誰也不會想到特雷西斯會出現在那裡。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line341", "option2": "line341"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒想過，有一天凱爾希醫生居然會傷得這麼重......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她總是會遊刃有餘地處理好一切問題，她總能給我們提供最恰當的建議。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她可是凱爾希醫生，我甚至從沒看到過她疲憊的樣子！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，現在......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "（牽住阿米婭的手）", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line355"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，我會擔負起我的責任。羅德島在這裡的使命還遠沒有結束。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在......我想再去看看凱爾希醫生，可以嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕是在她的床邊坐一會也好。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位，相比於陪護重傷患，你們現在有更重要的工作要做。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾讓我告訴你們，城防軍指揮塔上的那些數據已經解析完畢。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克洛維希婭正在召集一場會議。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要重新評估倫蒂尼姆的局勢了。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "戰爭爆發了。;我們的初步計劃失敗了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line368", "option2": "line368"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，告訴我們，下一步應該怎麼做。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "b